{"tid":1709964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府同港鐵遲d應該唔理鐵路有冇阻塞同安全問題，直接由佢引發嚴重交通事故","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T18:27:40.000Z","uid":73972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfd5353d428ea3e054d59d5f0f9ffc103059774","tid":1709964,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"照而加局勢咁睇，林鄭應該知點都分割唔到示威者同大部分普通市民，係佢心灰意冷之下，應該會任由港鐵忽略安全問題（港鐵紅磡出軌點野仲未解決），引發港鐵出軌事故，會死好多人，之後政府應該會借機歸咎示威者，令民心同國際輿論轉向<br />\n<br />\n我以後只會搭巴士"},{"pid":"570825b6f35aa5cbdc1d2b51e5bccf1ff653f145","tid":1709964,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ed4e25b0df9371461ff3c6b2a8285666b17062","tid":1709964,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:27:40.000Z","msg":"似"}]}